OL,4,Cfashion distribution centre set to
OL,5,Cclose
OL,7,FHundreds of people are set to lose
OL,8,Ftheir jobs as a major online fashion
OL,9,Fdistribution hub announces its closure.
OL,11,FRetailer Debenhams has confirmed plans
OL,12,Fto close its site in Burnley, instead
OL,13,Ftransferring operations to Sheffield.
OL,15,FBurnley Council leader Cllr Afrasiab
OL,16,FAnwar said the closure of the hub,
OL,17,Fcurrently on Heasandford Industrial
OL,18,FEstate on Widow Hill Road, was
OL,19,F"devastating for our town and for the
OL,20,Fhardworking employees and families who
OL,21,Fwill be directly affected".
