OL,7,FDebenhams was brought out of
OL,8,Fadministration in 2021 by BooHoo, in a
OL,9,F#51 million deal that made it an
OL,10,Fonline only retailer.
OL,12,FThe retailer has now confirmed the
OL,13,FBurnley operation - which currently
OL,14,Femploys 1,251 staff in several
OL,15,Fwarehouses in the area- will leave the
OL,16,Ftown in 2026.
